Activity1: Create a High Priority Student Application Notification Email Template 
Purpose: Notify the Counselor when a student application is identified as high priority by AI and requires immediate attention.

1. Go to Setup (gear icon on top-right).
2. In the Quick Find box, type Email Templates.
3. Click on Classic Email Templates.
4. Click New Template. Choose the type: Text – Plain text (no formatting) 
5. Click Next 

Template Name: High Priority Student Application Notification 
Subject: High-Priority Student Application Assigned to You 
Body: Hello {!Student_Enrollment__c.OwnerFullName},
A student application has been identified as high priority by AI and requires immediate attention.
Student Application Details:
Student Name: {!Student_Enrollment__c.Student__r.Name}
Course Applied: {!Student_Enrollment__c.Course__r.Name}
AI Priority Score: {!Student_Enrollment__c.AI_Priority_Score__c}
Enrollment Date: {!Student_Enrollment__c.Enrollment_Date__c}
Please contact the student and proceed with the admission process within 24 hours.
Thank you, AI-Enabled Student Admissions System 

6. Click on save

Activity2: Create a High Discount Student Enrollment Approval Email Template 
Purpose: Notify the Manager when a student enrollment with a high discount is submitted for approval.

1. Go to Setup (gear icon on top-right).
2. In the Quick Find box, type Email Templates.
3. Click on Classic Email Templates.
4. Click New Template. Choose the type: Text – Plain text (no formatting) 
5. Click Next 

Template Name: High Discount Student Enrollment Approval Notification 
Subject: Student Enrollment Awaiting Discount Approval 
Body: Hello {!Student_Enrollment__c.OwnerFullName},
A student enrollment with a high discount has been submitted for your approval.
Enrollment Details:
Student Name: {!Student_Enrollment__c.Student__r.Name}
Course Name: {!Student_Enrollment__c.Course__r.Name}
Course Fee: {!Student_Enrollment__c.Course__r.Course_Fee__c}
Discount Percentage: {!Student_Enrollment__c.Discount__c}%
Final Payable Amount: {!Student_Enrollment__c.Final_Payable_Amount__c}
Please review the enrollment details and approve or reject the request accordingly.
Thank you, Student Admissions Approval System 

6. Click on save

Activity3: Create a Student Enrollment Approval Outcome Notification Email Template 
Purpose: Notify the Counselor (Enrollment Owner) when a student enrollment is approved or rejected by the manager.

1. Go to Setup (gear icon on top-right).
2. In the Quick Find box, type Email Templates.
3. Click on Classic Email Templates.
4. Click New Template. 
5. Choose the type: Text – Plain text (no formatting) 
6. Click Next 

Template Name: Student Enrollment Approval Status Notification 
Subject: Student Enrollment Approval Decision \
Body: Hello {!Student_Enrollment__c.OwnerFullName},
The approval process for a student enrollment has been completed.
Enrollment Summary:
Student Name: {!Student_Enrollment__c.Student__r.Name}
Course Name: {!Student_Enrollment__c.Course__r.Name}
Approval Status: {!Student_Enrollment__c.Approval_Status__c}
Final Payable Amount: {!Student_Enrollment__c.Final_Payable_Amount__c}
Please proceed with the next steps in the admission process based on the approval outcome.
Thank you, Student Admissions Management System 

7.Click on save

